\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
态叠加原理
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Schrödinger 方程 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:量子态：Schrodinger 方程"

\end_inset

 关于波函数 
\begin_inset Formula $\psi$
\end_inset

 是线性的，因此有以下重要性质。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

[态叠加原理]
\end_layout

\end_inset

若波函数 
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{1},\psi_{2}$
\end_inset

 描述了某量子系统的两种许可态，则波函数 
\begin_inset Formula $c_{1}\psi_{1}+c_{2}\psi_{2}$
\end_inset

 亦为该系统的一种许可态，其中 
\begin_inset Formula $c_{1},c_{2}$
\end_inset

 为复常数。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Remark
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

[干涉]
\end_layout

\end_inset

一般而言，概率密度不满足叠加原理，而是遵循以下法则：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\abs{c_{1}\psi_{1}+c_{2}\psi_{2}}^{2} & =\Conj{(c_{1}\psi_{1}+c_{2}\psi_{2})}(c_{1}\psi_{1}+c_{2}\psi_{2})\\
 & =\underbrace{\Conj{(c_{1}\psi_{1})}(c_{1}\psi_{1})}_{\rho_{1}}+\underbrace{\Conj{(c_{2}\psi_{2})}(c_{2}\psi_{2})}_{\rho_{1}}+\underbrace{\Conj{(c_{1}\psi_{1})}(c_{2}\psi_{2})+\Conj{(c_{2}\psi_{2})}(c_{1}\psi_{1})}_{\rho_{1,2}}
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho_{1,2}$
\end_inset

 就体现了波的“干涉 (interference)”。
\end_layout

